Package: rservets
Title: Rserve wrappers for serving TypeScript-safe functions to JS apps
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Tom", "Elliott", , "tom.elliott@auckland.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7815-6318"))
Description: Provides methods for easier development of Typescript-safe 'Rserve' methods to integrate into JS apps (e.g., using ReactJS, NextJS), particularly user interfaces. Capabilities to generate typescript definition files and assert result types at run-time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
